1	//! Owned inline-array histogram.
2	//!
3	//! - `HistogramArray<N, C>` embeds its `[C; N]` counts, for
4	//!   callers who want one self-contained value (a static, a
5	//!   struct field) instead of managing a separate slice.
6	//! - Stable Rust cannot derive `N` from a `Config`'s powers
